### Polymarket + Odds API + Supabase REST quick-call sheet.
### Requires the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client).
### Env vars resolve from .env via `{{$dotenv VAR_NAME}}`.

@odds_key = {{$dotenv ODDS_API_KEY}}
@sb_url = {{$dotenv SUPABASE_URL}}
@sb_key = {{$dotenv SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY}}


### --- Polymarket Gamma API ---

### Active soccer markets (top 25)
GET https://gamma-api.polymarket.com/markets?active=true&closed=false&tag=Soccer&limit=25
Accept: application/json

### One market by slug
@market_slug = REPLACE_WITH_SLUG
GET https://gamma-api.polymarket.com/markets?slug={{market_slug}}
Accept: application/json


### --- Polymarket CLOB (order book) ---

### Order book for a YES/NO token
@token_id = REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_ID
GET https://clob.polymarket.com/book?token_id={{token_id}}
Accept: application/json

### Midpoint
GET https://clob.polymarket.com/midpoint?token_id={{token_id}}
Accept: application/json


### --- The Odds API ---

### Available sports
GET https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports?apiKey={{odds_key}}

### EPL h2h odds, Pinnacle only
GET https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports/soccer_epl/odds?apiKey={{odds_key}}&regions=eu&markets=h2h&bookmakers=pinnacle

### Champions League h2h odds, Pinnacle only
GET https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports/soccer_uefa_champs_league/odds?apiKey={{odds_key}}&regions=eu&markets=h2h&bookmakers=pinnacle

### Quota usage (response headers x-requests-remaining / x-requests-used)
GET https://api.the-odds-api.com/v4/sports?apiKey={{odds_key}}


### --- Supabase REST ---

### Row count: odds_api_snapshots
GET {{sb_url}}/rest/v1/odds_api_snapshots?select=id
apikey: {{sb_key}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sb_key}}
Prefer: count=exact
Range: 0-0

### Row count: polymarket_snapshots
GET {{sb_url}}/rest/v1/polymarket_snapshots?select=id
apikey: {{sb_key}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sb_key}}
Prefer: count=exact
Range: 0-0

### Most recent pinnacle row
GET {{sb_url}}/rest/v1/odds_api_snapshots?select=polled_at,home_team_id,away_team_id&bookmaker=eq.pinnacle&order=polled_at.desc&limit=1
apikey: {{sb_key}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sb_key}}

### Top unresolved entities
GET {{sb_url}}/rest/v1/unresolved_entities?select=raw_name,source,occurrences&order=occurrences.desc&limit=20
apikey: {{sb_key}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sb_key}}
